<template>
  <v-navigation-drawer v-model="drawer" width="250px"></v-navigation-drawer>
</template>
<script>
export default {
  name: "NavigationComponent",
  data() {
    return {
      drawer: false,
    };
  },
  methods: {
    openNavbar() {
      this.drawer = !this.drawer;
    },
  },
};
</script>
